					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">What are the timestamps (in ppu pixels) for the relevant bankswitch or ppu control instructions?
<br />
<br />The critical point is the two tile fetches at ppu pixel 5 and 7 (within the 8-cycle repeating sequence).  If the CPU write that triggers bankswitching completes before the two fetches happen, you get the wrong tiles.</div>

					
